data.description:
NEW PRICE!!! Nestled in the heart of the Lakeside Park community, 58 Arcadia Ave is a timeless blend of classic elegance and modern amenities. This picturesque 3-bedroom, 1 1/2 bath gem boasts a meticulous renovation, ensuring you experience both luxury and comfort. Step onto sumptuous new carpets and reinvigorated hardwood floors that gleam underfoot, leading you to a kitchen that's a culinary dream—completely remodeled and ready to inspire your inner chef.

Each room is painted in contemporary hues, offering a bright and airy ambiance, perfectly complemented by a state-of-the-art geo-thermal HVAC system ensuring year-round climate perfection. Imagine the possibilities with a spacious basement that holds the potential for transformation into a dynamic additional living space.

Safety and convenience go hand in hand with a detached one-car garage, offering both storage and protection for your vehicle. Set on a highly desirable street in Lakeside Park, this residence promises not just a house, but a home filled with cherished memories, laughter, and warmth.
